snippet.title: THE END IS NEAR 🔴LIVE - Death and Taxes (final episode)
snippet.description:
HOLO THERE! See you in the chat👀 2PM PT / 5PM ET Wednesday 
Join this channel for stream perks! Menchie Gang members are contributors to my monthly charity efforts😻 https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnaXc7HBuxqyP5fwOTH58FQ/join

Paint with me and use #paintwithsimply on socials to show me your mani!
Shop Holo Taco➡️ https://holota.co/simplystreamholo

00:00 - Stream starting soon
04:19 - HOLO! Stream starts and Simplygamelogical returns
07:41 - Streaming news and does my chat know Ludwig? 🤔
12:28 - Simply Not Logical memberships
15:02 - Membership data and November’s charity donations 💸
21:28 - Beyyyn’s mustache spooks Menchie 😱
24:44 - Simplystreamception: Watching Safiya and Tyler’s stream 
29:13 - Menchie stream takeover
32:12 - Poll: Who’s been following my grim reaper gameplay?
36:43 - Death and Taxes resumes on Day 26 and Beyyyn brings tea 
52:14 - Day 27: “Apocalypse Now” 🔥
1:08:27 - Day 28: “Only one choice left to make” 
1:15:50 - Poll: Should the Last Human live or die? 
1:27:00 - “Is this the end?!” 🤦‍♀️
1:31:19 - Researching other Death and Taxes endings
1:42:48 - Which games should I play next? 🎮
1:50:23 - Poll: Should I host sleeping Menchie streams? 
1:52:33 - wHaT’s oN mY nAiLs??? 💅
1:54:34 - Day 1 of 12 Days of Cristmas: Build Your Own Holo Taco Bundle 🎄
2:04:12 - Checking out games on Steam 
2:17:33 - Going off the rails 🤪
2:21:08 - Stream ends with Menchie; see y’all later chai! 

_ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _
